WEBVTT

00:01.001 --> 00:02.936
<i>LAST SEASON ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:02.970 --> 00:04.638
HE DIED OF A HEART ATTACK.
WE HAD A GOOD FIT.

00:04.671 --> 00:06.340
I WONDER HOW SHE'S GETTING BY.

00:06.373 --> 00:09.076
THE BIGGEST GAME IN THE PRIVATE
COMMUNITY OF AGRESTIC.

00:09.109 --> 00:11.478
DRUGS SELL THEMSELVES, BISCUIT.
YOU AIN'T SHIT.

00:11.512 --> 00:14.081
I HAVE TWO BOYS.
I'M NOT WITH THEM ENOUGH.

00:14.114 --> 00:16.383
SHANE SHOT A MOUNTAIN LION,
HE WROTE A GANGSTER RAP,

00:16.416 --> 00:18.085
NOW HE'S MAKING
TERRORIST VIDEOS.

00:18.118 --> 00:19.353
IS THIS YOUR SON?

00:19.386 --> 00:21.655
WE CAUGHT HIM AND HIS
GIRLFRIEND, HIGH ON SOMETHING.

00:21.688 --> 00:23.757
SHE'S IN THE CAR,
WON'T RESPOND TO ANY QUESTIONS.

00:23.790 --> 00:25.158
SHE'S DEAF.

00:25.192 --> 00:26.527
YOU FUCKING BETTER.

00:26.560 --> 00:29.162
UNCLE ANDY!
YES, I'M DIGGING THE LOVE.

00:29.196 --> 00:31.265
TOOK ME YEARS TO LEARN ‐‐

00:31.298 --> 00:33.300
SLIGHTLY DEFECTIVE CHICKS
ARE THE WAY TO GO.

00:33.333 --> 00:35.736
I ONCE WENT OUT WITH THIS GIRL
WITH A BABY ARM.

00:35.769 --> 00:37.538
INSANE IN THE SACK.

00:37.571 --> 00:40.407
PLUS WHEN SHE GRABBED MY DICK
WITH HER LITTLE HAND,

00:40.440 --> 00:41.275
IT LOOKED GIGANTIC.

00:41.308 --> 00:43.076
EVERYTHING YOU TOUCH
TURNS TO SHIT.

00:43.110 --> 00:45.412
WHATEVER YOU THINK ABOUT ME,
JUDAH WAS MY BROTHER.

00:45.445 --> 00:47.881
AND I HAVE YOUR BACK.
YOU NEED SOME HELP.

00:47.915 --> 00:49.283
Nancy:
I'M NOT A DEALER,

00:49.316 --> 00:52.286
I'M A MOTHER WHO HAPPENS TO
DISTRIBUTE ILLEGAL PRODUCTS

00:52.319 --> 00:56.156
THROUGH A SHAM BAKERY SET UP BY
MY ETHICALLY QUESTIONABLE CPA.

00:56.190 --> 00:57.524
Nancy:
YOU'RE ON THE CITY COUNCIL.

00:57.558 --> 00:59.760
WHAT IF SOMEONE LIKE CELIA
WALKED BY?

00:59.793 --> 01:00.994
RAGING BITCH.

01:01.028 --> 01:04.064
I WANT TO SEE MORE RUNNING
OUT THERE, ISABELLY.

01:04.565 --> 01:05.899
I HAVE CANCER.

01:05.933 --> 01:07.534
THE PUPPIES ARE COMING OFF,
NANCE.

01:07.568 --> 01:08.535
NICE HAIRCUT.

01:08.569 --> 01:09.536
IT'S A WIG.

01:09.570 --> 01:11.171
OH, RIGHT.
THE CANCER.

01:11.205 --> 01:13.140
HEY, BOSS.
I WAS JUST ABOUT TO LEAVE.

01:13.173 --> 01:15.008
I THINK YOU'RE REALLY,
REALLY PRETTY.

01:15.042 --> 01:16.777
WHEN DID YOU
START SMOKING?

01:16.810 --> 01:18.445
FUCK.
HEY!

01:18.478 --> 01:20.681
Nancy:
I GOT JACKED BY SOME CAMPUS COP.

01:20.714 --> 01:22.015
THIS IS YOURS.

01:22.049 --> 01:24.017
UH, I WANTED TO APOLOGIZE.

01:24.051 --> 01:26.286
Heylia:
I'M SURE YOU DIDN'T TELL HIM

01:26.320 --> 01:28.689
TO BEAT THE TAR OUT
OF LITTLE MR. SECURITY GUARD.

01:28.722 --> 01:29.923
YOU DID THAT?

01:29.957 --> 01:31.892
YOU WANT TO KEEP ON
DOING BUSINESS OVER HERE?

01:31.925 --> 01:34.027
YOU GONNA DO IT
WITH ME AND VANEETA.

01:34.061 --> 01:36.430
THAT'S CALLED THE RUNWAY.
THAT'S CALLED A TAINT ‐‐

01:36.463 --> 01:38.332
T'AIN'T ASS,
T'AIN'T EQUIPMENT.

01:38.365 --> 01:40.300
HEY, LUPITA,
WHAT DO YOU CALL THE THING

01:40.334 --> 01:42.069
BETWEEN THE DICK
AND THE ASSHOLE?

01:42.102 --> 01:43.270
THE COFFEE TABLE.

01:43.303 --> 01:46.406
THEY WANT TO SEND ME TO IRAQ,
LUPITA.

01:46.440 --> 01:47.374
BYE.

01:47.407 --> 01:48.342
FULL‐TIME STUDENTS

01:48.375 --> 01:50.310
WORKING TOWARD BECOMING
ORDAINED MINISTERS

01:50.344 --> 01:53.180
IN A RECOGNIZED RELIGION ARE
DEFERRED FROM MILITARY SERVICE.

01:53.213 --> 01:55.315
ONCE YOU GO RABBI,
YOU NEVER GO BYE‐BYE.

01:55.349 --> 01:56.416
MAZEL TOV.

01:56.450 --> 01:58.785
IN ORDER FOR US TO GROW,
WE HAVE TO GROW.

01:58.819 --> 02:00.153
WE DON'T NEED NO LAND.

02:00.187 --> 02:01.889
IT'S HYDRO.
ALL WE NEED IS WAREHOUSE SPACE.

02:01.922 --> 02:02.890
ENOUGH.

02:02.923 --> 02:04.024
YOU WORK FOR ME.

02:04.057 --> 02:05.259
WHAT'S THAT?

02:05.292 --> 02:07.694
60 DAYS TO HARVEST,
10 DAYS TO CURE ‐‐ HYDRO.

02:07.728 --> 02:11.265
GET RID OF THIS FUCKING BAKERY
AND LET US START A BUSINESS.

02:11.298 --> 02:13.667
HEYLIA WILL NEVER SPEAK
TO YOU AGAIN.
FUCK HEYLIA.

02:13.700 --> 02:15.102
Nancy:
I DON'T WANT TO CHOOSE

02:15.135 --> 02:16.904
BETWEEN MY BUSINESS
AND MY FAMILY.

02:16.937 --> 02:19.006
I WANT A RAISE.

02:19.039 --> 02:22.276
YOU MAY NOT TAKE THEM,
BUT YOU SURE DO SELL THEM.

02:22.309 --> 02:24.978
YOU GOT TO BE HONEST WITH YOUR
FAMILY ABOUT YOUR BUSINESS.

02:25.012 --> 02:26.346
WHAT'S GOING ON OUTSIDE?

02:26.380 --> 02:27.981
I INVITED
SOME FRIENDS OVER.

02:28.015 --> 02:30.017
WE'RE GOING TO GROW
MARIJUANA.

02:30.050 --> 02:33.320
DISTRIBUTION,
MEET FINANCE...

02:33.353 --> 02:35.222
SALES...

02:35.255 --> 02:36.557
LEGAL...

02:36.590 --> 02:37.824
YENTL.

02:37.858 --> 02:39.026
IF I HAVE TO PAY
FOR TETANUS,

02:39.059 --> 02:40.661
I WOULD BE THRILLED
TO PAY FOR IT.

02:40.694 --> 02:41.828
I'M PETER.

02:41.862 --> 02:43.063
YOU'RE CUTE.

02:43.096 --> 02:45.699
I WOULD REALLY LIKE
TO SEE YOU AGAIN,

02:45.732 --> 02:47.134
if ever you're ready.

02:50.170 --> 02:51.672
HI.

