05:24.625 --> 05:26.126
Peter: NANCY?

05:28.061 --> 05:29.730
JUST A MINUTE.

05:30.631 --> 05:32.432
[ TOILET FLUSHES ]

05:39.907 --> 05:41.542
GOD, YOU'RE BEAUTIFUL.

05:41.575 --> 05:42.609
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

05:42.643 --> 05:43.677
COME HERE.

05:45.712 --> 05:48.182
Shane: MOM?

05:49.550 --> 05:50.617
MOM?

05:59.393 --> 06:00.694
[ SNORING ]

06:07.367 --> 06:11.305
[ MOANING ]

06:21.048 --> 06:22.749
Peter:
CHECKING FOR MONSTERS?

06:22.783 --> 06:24.184
UH, OH.

06:24.218 --> 06:27.988
NO, I CAN'T FIND MY SHOE ‐‐
UH, SANDAL.

06:28.021 --> 06:29.923
IT'S A...SANDAL.

06:29.957 --> 06:32.559
SO I'M GUESSING
NO BREAKFAST.

06:32.593 --> 06:35.462
NO. I'M NOT REALLY
A BREAKFAST PERSON.

06:35.495 --> 06:37.464
I HAVE TO HAVE COFFEE
IN THE MORNING,

06:37.497 --> 06:39.933
BUT AFTER THAT,
I'M GOOD TILL LUNCH, USUALLY.

06:39.967 --> 06:43.604
SOMETIMES I HAVE
A BAGEL AROUND...10:30.

06:43.637 --> 06:44.938
I'LL MAKE YOU SOME COFFEE.

06:44.972 --> 06:46.740
UH, NO.
I SHOULD GO HOME.

06:46.773 --> 06:48.775
AHA.
FOUND IT.

06:48.809 --> 06:51.378
[ CHUCKLES ]

06:51.411 --> 06:53.747
YOU HAVE BIG FEET.

06:53.780 --> 06:56.917
WHY DO YOU HAVE A GUN
IN YOUR DRESSER?

06:56.950 --> 06:58.285
WERE YOU SNOOPING?

06:58.318 --> 06:59.987
MY FEET USED TO BE
SMALLER,

07:00.020 --> 07:01.922
BUT I WENT UP A SIZE
WITH EACH KID.

07:01.955 --> 07:04.358
IT'S JUST SITTING THERE
IN YOUR DRESSER.

07:04.391 --> 07:07.261
I SAW IT
WHEN I WENT TO PEE.

07:09.162 --> 07:11.265
I LIKE YOUR BIG FEET.

07:13.467 --> 07:16.803
THEY'RE NOT LIKE
FRED FLINTSTONE FEET.

07:16.837 --> 07:19.873
THEY'RE JUST...LONG.

07:19.907 --> 07:21.875
UH...

07:21.909 --> 07:26.046
WHAT DO YOU DO, EXACTLY...
FOR A LIVING?

07:26.079 --> 07:27.981
I'M A DEA AGENT.

07:28.015 --> 07:29.683
YOU NEVER SAID ANYTHING.

07:29.716 --> 07:30.918
YOU NEVER ASKED.

07:30.951 --> 07:33.687
AND IT'S NOT REALLY A JOB
THAT YOU ADVERTISE.

07:33.720 --> 07:34.688
I NEED TO GO HOME.

07:34.721 --> 07:36.790
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.
COME ON.

07:36.823 --> 07:38.025
WAIT.

07:38.058 --> 07:39.960
WAIT A SECOND.
[ Laughing ] YOU'RE NAKED.

07:39.993 --> 07:42.362
SO WERE YOU
UNTIL A FEW MINUTES AGO.

07:42.396 --> 07:45.299
BUT NOW IT'S DAYTIME, AND I'M
ALL DRESSED AND METHODIST.

07:45.332 --> 07:47.734
AH.
WELL, I NEED A GOODBYE KISS,

07:47.768 --> 07:48.836
OR I'LL FEEL...

07:48.869 --> 07:50.470
[ SNIFFS ]

07:50.504 --> 07:52.239
...CHEAP AND USED.

07:55.375 --> 07:56.944
SHOULD WE MAKE
ANOTHER DATE NOW?

07:56.977 --> 07:58.779
I'LL CALL YOU.

07:58.812 --> 08:00.347
DID MY GUN FREAK YOU OUT?

08:00.380 --> 08:01.882
YES.

08:01.915 --> 08:03.617
THE ONE ON THE DRESSER,
RIGHT?

08:03.650 --> 08:04.718
GOODBYE.

08:07.321 --> 08:12.259
♪♪ WHAT THE FUCK
WAS I THINKING? ♪♪

08:12.292 --> 08:16.396
♪♪ WHAT THE FUCK
WAS I THINKING? ♪♪

08:16.430 --> 08:20.601
♪♪ WHAT THE FUCK
WAS I THINKING? ♪♪

08:20.634 --> 08:21.869
LOOK AT THIS.

08:21.902 --> 08:23.737
WE'RE NEVER
GETTING OUT OF HERE.

08:23.770 --> 08:25.739
COULD YOU TURN ON
THE RADIO?

08:25.772 --> 08:27.274
I HAVE CALLED
THE CITY‐COUNCIL OFFICE

08:27.307 --> 08:30.577
OVER AND OVER ABOUT PUTTING IN
A LIGHT HERE.

08:30.611 --> 08:31.778
RADIO?

08:31.812 --> 08:34.748
NO, I CAN'T HAVE NOISE
RIGHT NOW.

08:34.781 --> 08:36.016
I'M TOO ANNOYED.

08:37.784 --> 08:39.253
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

08:39.286 --> 08:40.587
I'M HUNGRY.

08:40.621 --> 08:41.655
PLEASE!

08:41.688 --> 08:44.024
DON'T THINK I DIDN'T SEE YOU
EATING AND DRINKING

08:44.057 --> 08:46.159
EVERY SINGLE SAMPLE
IN THE STORE, MISS.

08:46.193 --> 08:48.128
CAN'T BELIEVE
THEY DIDN'T CUT YOU OFF

08:48.161 --> 08:49.796
AFTER THE SEVENTH
CHAI LATTE.

08:49.830 --> 08:51.598
THOSE CUPS ARE TINY.

08:51.632 --> 08:52.633
YEAH.
UNLIKE YOU.

08:52.666 --> 08:56.570
PUT THE PRETZELS BACK.
NO.

08:56.603 --> 08:58.005
THEN GIVE ME THE BAG.
NO.

08:58.038 --> 09:00.574
I AM THROWING THEM OUT.
NO, YOU'RE NOT! STOP!

09:00.607 --> 09:02.276
[ HORN HONKS ]

09:02.309 --> 09:04.645
SHIT.

09:04.678 --> 09:07.347
OH, GREAT.

09:07.381 --> 09:08.749
JUST PERFECT.

09:08.782 --> 09:10.484
[ CAR HORN HONKS ]

09:14.888 --> 09:16.356
SHIT.

09:16.390 --> 09:18.592
GOD DAMN IT.

09:18.625 --> 09:20.561
OH!

09:20.594 --> 09:22.029
OH, NO!

09:22.062 --> 09:23.897
SHE BE SO ANGRY.

09:23.931 --> 09:25.432
OH, NO, NO.
THIS IS NOT YOUR FAULT.

09:25.465 --> 09:27.401
YOU TELL THE MISSUS
IT'S YOUR FAULT.

09:27.434 --> 09:28.969
NO.
IT'S NOT MY FAULT, EITHER.

09:29.002 --> 09:30.504
Sí, IT'S YOUR FAULT.

09:30.537 --> 09:31.672
PLEASE, YOU TELL HER,

09:31.705 --> 09:34.007
OR SHE MAKE ME SLEEP WITH
THE DOG AND THE CORN SNAKE.

09:34.041 --> 09:36.777
THERE NEEDS TO BE
A TRAFFIC LIGHT.

09:36.810 --> 09:39.446
OH, THAT SNAKE, IT EAT DEAD RAT,
AND SHE MAKE ME KILL THE RAT.

09:39.479 --> 09:41.849
DOUG WILSON
AND HIS MERRY BAND OF IDIOTS

09:41.882 --> 09:43.784
JUST SITTING UP THERE
DOING NOTHING!

09:43.817 --> 09:45.552
SHE LOVE THIS CAR.

09:45.586 --> 09:48.121
EVERY MONTH, SHE PAY MORE
FOR THIS CAR THAN FOR ME.

09:48.155 --> 09:49.423
AND I HAVE NO LICENSE.

09:49.456 --> 09:52.192
YOU HAVE NO LICENSE?
OH, THAT'S FABULOUS.

09:52.226 --> 09:54.127
ARE YOU EVEN LEGAL?
WHAT'S YOUR NAME?

09:54.161 --> 09:55.963
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.
LET ME GET A PEN.

09:55.996 --> 09:58.165
STAY RIGHT HERE.

09:58.198 --> 10:00.634
WHO'S YOUR MISSUS?

10:00.667 --> 10:01.602
Isabel: MOM?

10:01.635 --> 10:02.603
ONE SECOND.

10:02.636 --> 10:04.404
NO. MOM!
MOM!

10:04.438 --> 10:05.973
ONE SECOND!

10:06.006 --> 10:07.374
OH, SHIT.

10:07.407 --> 10:08.976
THANK YOU.

10:15.182 --> 10:17.284
DO YOU REALIZE
IF I MARRIED A NON‐JEW,

10:17.317 --> 10:19.219
I COULDN'T GO
TO RABBINICAL SCHOOL?

10:19.253 --> 10:21.188
I CAN GO IF I'M GAY
AND MY LOVER'S JEWISH.

10:21.221 --> 10:22.456
I CAN GO IF I'M SINGLE.

10:22.489 --> 10:25.626
BUT I'M NOT ELIGIBLE
IF I MARRY A BEAUTIFUL SHIKSA

10:25.659 --> 10:28.295
WITH BLOND, SILKY PUBES

10:28.328 --> 10:30.197
WAXED INTO THE SHAPE
OF A SHAMROCK.

10:30.230 --> 10:32.132
DOESN'T THAT SEEM FUCKED UP
TO YOU?

10:32.165 --> 10:34.835
I MEAN, MORE THAN HALF
OF ALL AMERICAN JEWS

10:34.868 --> 10:36.036
MARRY OUTSIDE THE TRIBE.

10:36.069 --> 10:37.538
CLEARLY THERE'S A PROBLEM.

10:37.571 --> 10:39.139
AND YET WHEN A JEWISH PERSON

10:39.173 --> 10:41.842
IS INTERESTED IN PURSUING
HIS OR HER RELIGIOUS CALLING,

10:41.875 --> 10:45.012
IF HE OR SHE FELL IN LOVE WITH
SOMEONE OUTSIDE THE FAITH ‐‐

10:45.045 --> 10:48.015
AND LORD KNOWS, WE DON'T ALWAYS
CHOOSE WHO TO LOVE ‐‐

10:48.048 --> 10:51.752
THAT JEW IS TURNED AWAY.

10:51.785 --> 10:53.320
HOW WAS YOUR SLEEPOVER?

10:53.353 --> 10:55.022
YEAH, HOW WAS YOUR SLEEPOVER,
NANCY?

10:55.055 --> 10:56.423
DID YOU THINK
TO LET ANYONE KNOW

10:56.456 --> 10:58.659
YOU WERE TAKING OFF
FOR THE NIGHT?

10:58.692 --> 11:00.594
YES, I DID.

11:00.627 --> 11:03.363
BOTH ANDY AND LUPITA KNEW
HOW TO GET IN TOUCH WITH ME,

11:03.397 --> 11:07.568
AND I DON'T HAVE TO DEFEND
MY ACTIONS TO MY TEENAGE CHILD.

11:07.601 --> 11:08.869
I GOT SCARED.

11:08.902 --> 11:10.704
HONEY, YOU WERE ASLEEP.

11:10.737 --> 11:11.872
I WOKE UP.

11:11.905 --> 11:13.540
SWEETIE, I'M SORRY.

11:13.574 --> 11:15.843
I DIDN'T MEAN
TO MAKE YOU NERVOUS, OKAY?

11:15.876 --> 11:18.212
I WAS JUST AT
A FRIEND'S HOUSE.

11:20.514 --> 11:21.882
THE DISHWASHER'S BROKEN.

11:21.915 --> 11:23.217
HMM.

11:23.250 --> 11:24.518
LUPITA!

11:24.551 --> 11:26.854
MAYBE IF YOU SPEND
MORE TIME AROUND HERE,

11:26.887 --> 11:28.689
YOU MIGHT KNOW THAT.

11:28.722 --> 11:31.124
WOULD YOU PLEASE
DO THE DISHES?

11:31.158 --> 11:32.860
MACHINE IS BROKE.

11:32.893 --> 11:34.294
I KNOW THAT.

11:34.328 --> 11:36.463
THAT'S WHY I'D LIKE YOU
TO DO THE DISHES.

11:36.496 --> 11:37.731
OH, NO.

11:37.764 --> 11:38.966
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, NO?

11:38.999 --> 11:40.434
MAKES MY HANDS CRACK.

11:40.467 --> 11:42.135
YOU NEED TO GET
THE MACHINE FIXED.

11:42.169 --> 11:44.137
MAYBE I NEED TO GET
A NEW HOUSEKEEPER.

11:44.171 --> 11:47.941
MAYBE YOU HAVE TOO MUCH LOVE
AND TRUST FOR ME

11:47.975 --> 11:49.710
TO EVER LET ME GO.

11:55.182 --> 11:56.283
CALL THE REPAIR GUY

11:56.316 --> 11:58.385
AND GET HIM OVER HERE
AS SOON AS POSSIBLE.

11:58.418 --> 11:59.953
OKAY.

11:59.987 --> 12:02.256
SO, IS THIS GONNA BE
A REGULAR THING WITH YOU?

12:02.289 --> 12:03.891
WHAT IS WITH YOUR TONE?

12:03.924 --> 12:05.158
MORNING.

12:05.192 --> 12:07.895
YOU'RE NOT WEARING
ANY PANTS.

12:07.928 --> 12:10.030
THAT'S OKAY.
I'M ALMOST A RABBI.

12:10.063 --> 12:12.232
SHANE'S NOT, AND YOU'RE
A LAWSUIT WAITING TO HAPPEN.

12:12.266 --> 12:13.901
GO UPSTAIRS,
PUT SOME CLOTHES ON.

12:13.934 --> 12:15.068
SORRY.

12:15.102 --> 12:16.870
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

12:16.904 --> 12:18.605
LUPITA, WOULD YOU GET THAT,
PLEASE?

12:19.940 --> 12:22.476
I DIDN'T SAY THAT MEGAN
COULD SLEEP OVER.

12:22.509 --> 12:24.745
THEY DIDN'T DO
MUCH SLEEPING.
EXCUSE ME?

12:24.778 --> 12:26.280
SHUT UP, YOU SPYING PERV!

12:26.313 --> 12:28.749
I WAS LOOKING FOR MOM.
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT ‐‐

12:28.782 --> 12:31.051
AN AMAZING ACCIDENT.

12:31.852 --> 12:33.153
I DON'T EVEN WANT TO KNOW.

12:33.187 --> 12:35.355
YOU DIDN'T TELL ME
SHE COULDN'T SLEEP OVER.

12:35.389 --> 12:36.690
COME ON, NANCY.

12:36.723 --> 12:38.125
STOP CALLING ME NANCY.

12:38.158 --> 12:41.662
MY NAME IS MOM,
OR MOMMY DEAREST.

12:41.695 --> 12:44.164
"FOR BEAUTIFUL NANCY

12:44.198 --> 12:47.334
"WITH THE LONG, ELEGANT FEET.

12:47.367 --> 12:48.135
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:48.168 --> 12:50.404
"DON'T BE AFRAID.
PETER."

12:50.437 --> 12:52.005
EW.
FEET?

12:52.039 --> 12:54.341
NICE WORK, MOMMY DEAREST.

12:54.374 --> 12:57.110
OH, DEAR GOD.

13:01.248 --> 13:05.185
WERE YOU MEAN TO YOUR MOTHER
WHEN YOU WERE A TEENAGER?

13:05.219 --> 13:07.287
I DIDN'T LIVE WITH MY MOM.
I LIVED WITH HEYLIA.

13:07.321 --> 13:09.256
AND YOU DON'T PULL THAT SHIT
WITH HEYLIA.

13:09.289 --> 13:11.258
I WANT MY KIDS TO FEAR ME.

13:11.291 --> 13:13.327
CAN DO WHAT MY MOMS DID.

13:13.360 --> 13:14.595
WHICH WAS?

13:14.628 --> 13:15.863
SHE SHOT ME IN THE LEG.

13:15.896 --> 13:17.731
ARE YOU SERIOUS?

13:17.764 --> 13:20.601
SHE SHOT ME IN THE LEG, AND I AM
AFRAID OF THAT WOMAN NOW.

13:20.634 --> 13:22.269
WAS SHE ON DRUGS?

13:22.302 --> 13:24.471
MY MOM NEVER DID A DRUG
A DAY IN HER LIFE.

13:24.505 --> 13:26.440
MY MOM WAS A DRUNK.

13:26.473 --> 13:29.977
ONE NIGHT SHE THOUGHT
THAT I WAS MY POPS.

13:30.010 --> 13:31.879
THAT'S HOW WE GOT INTO
THE DRUG GAME.

13:31.912 --> 13:33.814
THE PAIN‐KILLERS
I WAS GETTING FROM THE DOCTOR

13:33.847 --> 13:35.182
WAS MAKING ME SLEEP
ALL THE TIME,

13:35.215 --> 13:36.416
SO HEYLIA SWITCHED ME
TO WEED

13:36.450 --> 13:38.519
AND STARTED MEETING PEOPLE
IN THE INDUSTRY.

13:38.552 --> 13:39.419
AH.

13:39.453 --> 13:41.588
BEFORE THAT,
SHE WORKED AT PRICE CLUB.

13:41.622 --> 13:45.225
HEY, TEAM, YOU SOLVE
ALL OUR PROBLEMS YET?

13:45.259 --> 13:47.628
MIGHT SHOOT SILAS
IN THE LEG.

13:47.661 --> 13:49.630
[ LAUGHS ]

13:49.663 --> 13:52.432
LOOK, RIGHT NOW,
IF WE LIQUIDATED EVERYTHING,

13:52.466 --> 13:53.901
GOT OURSELVES
OUT OF THE LEASE,

13:53.934 --> 13:55.869
WE'RE LOOKING AT MAYBE HALF
OF WHAT WE NEED

13:55.903 --> 13:58.105
TO START GROWING MARIJUANA.

13:59.706 --> 14:02.476
WHAT ABOUT INSURANCE?

14:02.509 --> 14:04.411
YOU GOT SOME KIND
OF SNEAKY ARSON PLOT

14:04.444 --> 14:06.847
BEHIND THEM CRAZY EYES?
COULD WE?

14:06.880 --> 14:08.549
BABY, THAT SHIT ONLY WORK
ON "THE SOPRANOS."

14:08.582 --> 14:10.417
AND I WILL GUARANTEE YOU
THAT THE FIRE CHIEF

14:10.450 --> 14:11.985
IS BETTER
AT INVESTIGATING ARSON

14:12.019 --> 14:13.887
THAN YOU ARE
AT COMMITTING IT.

14:13.921 --> 14:16.356
YOU ARE A DRUG DEALER.

14:17.925 --> 14:19.126
NOT A FIREBUG.

14:19.159 --> 14:21.495
WHY DO YOU GET TO CALL
NANCY "BABY" AND I DON'T?

14:21.528 --> 14:23.096
BLACK THING.

14:24.264 --> 14:25.199
FINE.

14:25.232 --> 14:29.036
CAN I GET A LITTLE HELP HERE,
PLEASE?

14:34.808 --> 14:37.144
ANYWAY...

14:37.177 --> 14:38.879
BABY, WE GOT SOME PROBLEMS.

14:38.912 --> 14:40.614
YEAH.

14:40.647 --> 14:44.751
DID I MENTION I SLEPT WITH
A DEA AGENT LAST NIGHT?

14:50.657 --> 14:51.959
I'M NOT GOING TO JAIL
FOR YOU!

14:51.992 --> 14:52.993
FUCK THIS!
I'M OUT!

14:53.026 --> 14:54.862
CONRAD, HE DOESN'T KNOW.

14:54.895 --> 14:57.731
MY KID BIT HIS KID'S FOOT
IN KARATE.

14:57.764 --> 14:58.932
HOW COULD HE PLAN THAT?

14:58.966 --> 15:01.602
IT'S JUST A TOTALLY FUCKED UP,
RANDOM THING.

15:01.635 --> 15:03.804
HE CAME OUT TOLD ME
WHAT HE DOES FOR A LIVING.

15:03.837 --> 15:04.872
HE DOESN'T KNOW!

15:04.905 --> 15:05.873
FUCK, HE DOESN'T KNOW.

15:05.906 --> 15:07.040
AND EVEN IF HE DOESN'T,
HE WILL.

15:07.074 --> 15:08.275
AND ME, I'M GONNA BE GONE.

15:08.308 --> 15:10.911
DO NOT COME AROUND HEYLIA'S.
DO YOU HEAR ME?

15:10.944 --> 15:12.145
YOU HAVE STEPPED IN SHIT,

15:12.179 --> 15:14.448
AND YOU AIN'T GONNA TRACK IT
THROUGH MY HOUSE.

15:14.481 --> 15:16.350
CONRAD, I WON'T TALK
TO HIM ANYMORE.

15:16.383 --> 15:17.351
IT'S TOO LATE.

15:17.384 --> 15:19.119
OKAY, OKAY.

15:19.152 --> 15:20.554
HEY.

15:20.587 --> 15:23.023
ARE YOU ANGRY
'CAUSE I FUCKED A DEA AGENT

15:23.056 --> 15:25.292
OR BECAUSE I FUCKED
SOMEBODY ELSE?

15:25.325 --> 15:26.793
OH, WOW.

15:26.827 --> 15:29.796
YOU THINK THIS ABOUT
YOUR ARROGANT ASS.

15:29.830 --> 15:31.131
LET ME TELL YOU SOMETHING.

15:31.164 --> 15:33.500
WE WOULDN'T BE HAVING
THIS CONVERSATION RIGHT NOW

15:33.534 --> 15:35.469
IF YOU'D HAVE FUCKED
A TRAVEL AGENT.

15:37.638 --> 15:40.107
GET OUT MY WAY.

15:48.415 --> 15:53.020
I HAVE ASKED EVERY WAY
THAT I KNOW HOW.

15:53.053 --> 15:55.856
YOU HAVE REPEATEDLY IGNORED
MY REQUESTS.

15:55.889 --> 15:58.392
BUT IT DOES NOT CHANGE
THE FACT

15:58.425 --> 16:02.362
THAT THERE NEEDS TO BE A LIGHT
AT THE INTERSECTION.

16:02.396 --> 16:05.499
IT'S A MATTER OF PUBLIC SAFETY.

16:05.532 --> 16:07.968
WHAT IS?

16:08.001 --> 16:09.970
THE LIGHT.

16:10.003 --> 16:11.338
CELIA, LIGHTS COST MONEY.

16:11.371 --> 16:14.208
YES. ISN'T THAT WHAT THE BUDGET
IS FOR, DOUG?

16:14.241 --> 16:16.276
ALL OF OUR MONEY HAS BEEN
ALLOCATED FOR THE YEAR.

16:16.310 --> 16:18.011
WE'RE RENOVATING
THIS CHAMBER HERE.

16:18.045 --> 16:19.880
HAVEN'T YOU SEEN THE PLANS?
I MEAN, COME ON.

16:19.913 --> 16:22.015
WE GOT A FULL KITCHEN
GOING IN BACK THERE.

16:22.049 --> 16:25.352
SO I PAY MY TAXES
SO YOU CAN HAVE A KITCHEN?

16:25.385 --> 16:26.386
AND A PARADE.

16:26.420 --> 16:28.822
AND THE BALANCE OF WHAT WE OWE
THE BRANDING FIRM

16:28.856 --> 16:30.023
FOR THE NEW TOWN SLOGAN,

16:30.057 --> 16:32.593
"AGRESTIC ‐‐
THE BEST OF THE BEST‐IC," HUH?

16:32.626 --> 16:34.094
AND A LOT OF OTHER STUFF.

16:34.127 --> 16:35.762
A LOT OF OTHER STUFF, TOO.

16:35.796 --> 16:36.930
NOW, IF THAT'S EVERYTHING,

16:36.964 --> 16:38.732
I WANT TO GO HOME
AND WATCH THE GAME

16:38.765 --> 16:40.634
AND DRINK A LITTLE BIT.

16:40.667 --> 16:41.702
ADJOURNED.

16:41.735 --> 16:42.769
OH, HEY, MITCH....

16:42.803 --> 16:44.271
YOUR TURN TO BRING SNACKS
NEXT WEEK.

16:44.304 --> 16:46.273
I THINK I SPEAK FOR EVERYONE
WHEN I SAY

16:46.306 --> 16:49.977
VEGETARIAN PIGS IN A BLANKET
ARE BULLSHIT.

16:52.379 --> 16:54.147
OOH!

16:54.181 --> 16:56.149
CELIA.
I'M SORRY.

16:56.183 --> 16:59.152
ALTHOUGH I DO THINK THAT COUNTS
AS A TOUCHDOWN.

16:59.186 --> 17:03.323
[ MACHINE HISSING ]

17:06.159 --> 17:09.062
WANT A SHOT OF JACK
IN THAT?

17:10.564 --> 17:11.932
OH, I READ THAT.

17:11.965 --> 17:13.200
GREAT ARTICLE

17:13.233 --> 17:15.569
ABOUT INJECTING HUMAN
GROWTH HORMONE TO STAY YOUNG.

17:15.602 --> 17:18.272
EXCEPT THEY NEVER SAY
WHERE THEY'RE GETTING IT FROM.

17:18.305 --> 17:20.407
MAKES YOU WONDER
IF THEY'RE SUCKING THE YOUTH

17:20.440 --> 17:22.276
OUT OF SMALL,
BROWN CHILDREN SOMEWHERE

17:22.309 --> 17:25.646
SO THAT ACTORS AND TROPHY WIVES
CAN STAY IN BUSINESS.

17:25.679 --> 17:28.282
I was serious
about the shot.

17:28.315 --> 17:29.349
YOU WANT?

17:29.383 --> 17:30.851
ACTUALLY, I DO.

17:30.884 --> 17:33.086
IT'S BEEN ONE OF THOSE DAYS.

17:33.120 --> 17:35.389
SO, YOU HEARD ABOUT
MY ACCIDENT, RIGHT?

17:35.422 --> 17:37.791
AND I JUST GOT HUMILIATED
AT CITY COUNCIL

17:37.824 --> 17:40.727
BY THE FUCKHEAD,
DOUG WILSON.

17:40.761 --> 17:42.029
SO, WHAT'S UP WITH YOU?

17:42.062 --> 17:43.564
JUST LIFE ‐‐

17:43.597 --> 17:45.199
KIDS.

17:46.400 --> 17:47.401
BAKING.

17:47.434 --> 17:48.869
YOU NEED TO GET LAID.

17:48.902 --> 17:50.404
FRANKLY, SO DO I.

17:50.437 --> 17:52.906
ARE YOU SEEING ANYONE?
MAYBE WE COULD SHARE.

17:52.940 --> 17:55.475
YOU SHOULD RUN
FOR CITY COUNCIL.

17:55.509 --> 17:57.144
DOUG WOULD LOSE HIS MIND.

17:57.177 --> 17:59.313
OH, I DIDN'T MEAN RUN FOR ‐‐
FOR DOUG'S SEAT.

17:59.346 --> 18:01.782
YEAH, BUT DOUG'S SEAT
IS UP THIS YEAR.

18:01.815 --> 18:03.217
YEAH.
MAYBE IT WAS A BAD IDEA.

18:03.250 --> 18:05.419
NO, I THINK IT'S
A PERFECTLY GREAT IDEA.

18:05.452 --> 18:08.422
SHOW THAT ASSHOLE THAT HE CAN'T
TREAT PEOPLE LIKE SHIT

18:08.455 --> 18:12.259
AND IGNORE THEIR TOTALLY
REASONABLE REQUESTS.

18:12.292 --> 18:14.061
I'M RUNNING
FOR CITY COUNCIL.

18:14.094 --> 18:14.895
THANK YOU, NANCY.
I FEEL SO MUCH BETTER NOW.

18:14.928 --> 18:18.498
♪♪ BUH‐BUH BUH BUH ♪♪

18:22.269 --> 18:24.905
SO BASICALLY, MY WHOLE LIFE'S
BEEN LEADING UP TO THIS ‐‐

18:24.938 --> 18:26.974
TO HERE,
TO THE RABBINATE.

18:27.007 --> 18:29.243
YOU KNOW,
IT'S MY TRUE CALLING.

18:30.811 --> 18:33.480
AND AS FAR AS THE HEBREW GOES,
I'M A REALLY QUICK STUDY.

18:33.514 --> 18:36.016
I KNOW ALL
THE "BARUCH ATAHS" ALREADY,

18:36.049 --> 18:39.686
AND I KNOW THE WORD
FOR "JELLYFISH" IS "MEDUZOT."

18:39.720 --> 18:43.423
AND "GLIDA,"
THAT'S "ICE CREAM."

18:43.457 --> 18:46.093
DO YOU KNOW WHAT
"ZAYAN SECHEL" MEANS,

18:46.126 --> 18:50.364
AS IN, "ANI CHO‐SHEVET
SHEY ATA ZAYAN SECHEL"?

18:50.397 --> 18:52.866
NO.
I DON'T THINK I KNOW THAT ONE.

18:52.900 --> 18:55.602
OKAY.
SO, THIS HAS BEEN VERY AMUSING.

18:55.636 --> 18:58.505
I WISH YOU ALL THE BEST
IN YOUR LIFE, AND NOW I'M DONE.

18:58.539 --> 19:00.574
WAIT.
WHAT?! I'M IN?

19:00.607 --> 19:01.542
YOU TALK A LOT.

19:01.575 --> 19:03.877
THAT'S A WONDERFUL QUALITY
IN A RABBI, NO?

19:03.911 --> 19:05.612
AND YET YOU SAY NOTHING.

19:05.646 --> 19:06.613
OH, HO!

19:06.647 --> 19:07.915
ISRAELI SNAP!

19:07.948 --> 19:09.149
THAT'S OKAY,
I CAN TAKE IT.

19:09.183 --> 19:11.718
RESILIENCY IS ANOTHER
EXCELLENT RABBINIC TRAIT.

19:11.752 --> 19:14.388
TIME FOR YOU TO GO.
OKAY?

19:14.421 --> 19:15.889
GOODBYE.

19:15.923 --> 19:18.258
OKAY. GOOD.
THANKS FOR YOUR TIME.

19:18.292 --> 19:20.494
UM, I GUESS
I'M GONNA HAVE TO...

19:20.527 --> 19:21.395
[ CHUCKLES ]

19:21.428 --> 19:23.297
...LOOK FOR ANOTHER
RABBINICAL SCHOOL,

19:23.330 --> 19:25.766
ONE THAT RESPECTS
MY AMBITION,

19:25.799 --> 19:27.701
ONE THAT RECOGNIZES
MY TALENT.

19:27.734 --> 19:29.603
YES. OUR LOSS.
GOOD LUCK TO YOU.

19:32.306 --> 19:34.975
I'M BEGGING YOU.
THIS IS THE END OF THE ROAD.

19:35.008 --> 19:37.411
IF YOU DON'T LET ME
INTO YOUR SCHOOL,

19:37.444 --> 19:38.545
I'M GONNA BE KILLED.

19:38.579 --> 19:39.479
REALLY?

19:39.513 --> 19:41.548
SOMEONE HOLDING A GUN
TO YOUR HEAD, SAYING,

19:41.582 --> 19:43.116
"BE A RABBI OR DIE"?

19:47.387 --> 19:48.889
ACTUALLY, YEAH.

19:48.922 --> 19:50.724
YOU'RE MY LAST CHANCE,
YAEL HOFFMAN,

19:50.757 --> 19:52.759
DIRECTOR OF ADMISSIONS.

19:54.595 --> 19:56.396
I BESEECH YOU.

19:57.664 --> 19:59.933
MY LIFE IS IN YOUR HANDS.

19:59.967 --> 20:02.703
YOU HAVE FIVE MINUTES
TO EXPLAIN YOURSELF,

20:02.736 --> 20:04.004
AND NO MORE BULLSHIT.

20:04.037 --> 20:06.073
AND I'M WEARING A BRA,

20:06.106 --> 20:08.008
SO STOP LOOKING
FOR MY NIPPLES.

20:08.041 --> 20:09.743
THAT ‐‐
HOW'D YOU KNOW?

20:09.776 --> 20:10.878
4 MINUTES, 50 SECONDS.

20:10.911 --> 20:12.246
OKAY.

20:17.484 --> 20:20.787
I DIDN'T CARE WHAT SHIT
WAS GOING ON.

20:20.821 --> 20:23.023
EVERY NIGHT,
WE HAD FAMILY DINNER.

20:23.056 --> 20:24.558
WE WERE TALKING ABOUT
OUR DAY,

20:24.591 --> 20:27.094
ARGUING, OR GIVING EACH OTHER
THE STINK EYE.

20:27.127 --> 20:28.629
WHATEVER,
WE WERE ALL HERE.

20:28.662 --> 20:31.398
ALL SORTS OF STUDIES
TALK ABOUT HOW FAMILY DINNER

20:31.431 --> 20:33.767
IS LIKE SUPERGLUE ‐‐
HOLD YOU TOGETHER

20:33.800 --> 20:35.369
AND FIXES EVERYTHING
THAT'S BROKE.

20:35.402 --> 20:38.038
YEP. HIGHER TEST SCORES,
LESS DEPRESSION.

20:38.071 --> 20:39.506
YOU GUYS ARE BETTER
THAN NPR.

20:39.540 --> 20:43.343
OH, WE THE ORIGINAL NPR ‐‐
NEGROES PREACHING RIGHT.

20:43.377 --> 20:44.244
MM‐HMM.

20:44.278 --> 20:45.579
AND IF DINNER DON'T WORK,

20:45.612 --> 20:48.015
YOU NEED TO SMACK SOME SENSE
INTO THAT BOY.

20:48.048 --> 20:50.017
I'M NOT MUCH FOR SMACKING.

20:50.050 --> 20:51.718
JUST DON'T BE HIS BITCH.

20:51.752 --> 20:53.120
YOU PUSHED HIM OUT
YOUR HOOTCH.

20:53.153 --> 20:54.755
YOU CAN PUSH HIM OUT
YOUR HOUSE.

20:54.788 --> 20:56.023
YOU THE BOSS.

20:56.056 --> 20:57.057
LET'S SEE.

20:57.090 --> 20:59.493
YOU WANT GRUYèRE
OR SMOKED GOUDA?

20:59.526 --> 21:00.794
SMOKED GOUDA.

21:00.827 --> 21:05.132
SO, UH, IS CONRAD AROUND?

21:05.165 --> 21:07.167
NOW, YOU ABOUT TO LOSE
YOUR PANINI.

21:07.201 --> 21:08.869
YOU KNOW YOU AIN'T FRIENDS
NO MORE.

21:08.902 --> 21:09.903
THEM'S THE RULES.

21:09.937 --> 21:11.104
I JUST THOUGHT ‐‐

21:11.138 --> 21:12.840
HE OUT BUYING ME
A BREAST PUMP.

21:12.873 --> 21:14.775
I HOPE HE'S GETTING YOU
ELECTRIC.

21:14.808 --> 21:16.376
THE MANUAL TAKES FOREVER.

21:16.410 --> 21:18.612
SHIT.
DID WE SAY ELECTRIC OR MANUAL?

21:18.645 --> 21:19.746
WE DIDN'T SAY NOTHING.

21:19.780 --> 21:22.249
AND DON'T THINK THAT I'M
GOING TO SIT UP IN THIS HOUSE

21:22.282 --> 21:24.918
WHILE YOU OUT THERE SHOWING OFF
YOUR BRAND‐NEW TITTIES.

21:24.952 --> 21:27.087
I GOT A LIFE, TOO,
YOU KNOW.

21:27.120 --> 21:28.222
[ BABY CRYING ]

21:28.255 --> 21:30.324
Conrad:
WHAT THE HELL IS SHE DOING HERE?

21:30.357 --> 21:31.558
IS THAT THE MANUAL?
UNH‐UNH.

21:31.592 --> 21:34.027
NO. SEE, YOU GONNA HAVE TO
TAKE THAT BACK.

21:34.061 --> 21:35.762
I NEED THE ‐‐
WHAT DO I NEED?

21:35.796 --> 21:37.130
THE PUMP IN STYLE.

21:37.164 --> 21:39.833
PUMP IN STYLE.
ELECTRIC.

21:39.867 --> 21:41.969
OH, THIS LOOKS DELICIOUS,
HEYLIA.

21:42.002 --> 21:44.104
CAN I TRY THE GRUYèRE
NEXT TIME I COME?

21:44.137 --> 21:45.639
AIN'T GONNA BE
NO NEXT TIME.

21:45.672 --> 21:48.642
HEYLIA, CONRAD'S TALKING TO ME,
AND HE'S NOT SUPPOSED TO.

21:48.675 --> 21:49.643
THAT'S RIGHT.

21:49.676 --> 21:51.845
BOY, GET YOUR BLACK ASS
BACK OUT TO THAT STORE

21:51.879 --> 21:53.480
AND GET THIS GIRL THE, UH...
PUMP IN STYLE.

21:53.514 --> 21:55.682
THE PUMP IN STYLE.
AND HERE. TAKE THIS.

21:55.716 --> 21:57.184
GO ON.

22:00.921 --> 22:02.256
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

22:03.790 --> 22:04.791
ALL RIGHT.

22:04.825 --> 22:06.026
SO WHAT ABOUT,

22:06.059 --> 22:09.630
"CELIA HODES ‐‐
IT'S TIME FOR CHANGE"?

22:09.663 --> 22:11.632
AND THEN WE SHOW
A BIG CLOCK,

22:11.665 --> 22:12.566
AND INSTEAD OF NUMBERS,

22:12.599 --> 22:14.535
THERE ARE NICKELS AND DIMES
AND QUARTERS.

22:14.568 --> 22:17.137
GET IT? "TIME FOR CHANGE."
ISN'T THAT CUTE?

22:17.171 --> 22:19.373
YEAH, THAT'S RETARDED.
THAT IS NOT VERY NICE.

22:19.406 --> 22:22.709
I HAVE A NEPHEW WHO'S RETARDED,
AND HE HAS TO WEAR A HELMET.

22:22.743 --> 22:24.144
WHERE ARE THE OTHER GIRLS?

22:24.178 --> 22:25.546
DIDN'T WE SAY 4:30?

22:25.579 --> 22:28.015
THEY'RE NOT COMING, CELIA.
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

22:28.048 --> 22:30.551
NO, NO, NO, NO,
THIS IS ABOUT AGRESTIC.

22:30.584 --> 22:33.554
I AM SO CLEARLY MORE QUALIFIED
THAN DOUG WILSON.

22:33.587 --> 22:36.156
THEY TAKE STRIPPER‐FITNESS CLASS
WITH DOUG'S WIFE, DANA.

22:36.190 --> 22:37.758
IT'S A WHOLE BONDING THING.

22:37.791 --> 22:39.793
STRIPPER‐FITNESS CLASS?

22:39.826 --> 22:41.261
KENNETH DOESN'T LIKE ME
TO DO IT

22:41.295 --> 22:43.096
'CAUSE HE THINKS I'LL GO LESBO
ON HIM,

22:43.130 --> 22:44.431
LIKE WHEN I TOOK FOLK GUITAR.

22:44.464 --> 22:47.234
HELLO, LADIES.
HOW'S THE ELECTION PLANNING?

22:47.267 --> 22:49.603
OH, FINE.
TRYING TO FIND A SLOGAN.

22:49.636 --> 22:50.838
NO, NO, NO, NO,
NO, NO, NO.

22:50.871 --> 22:52.472
THAT'S GROWN‐UP JUICE.
NOT FOR YOU.

22:52.506 --> 22:54.541
WELL, WHEN CAN I HAVE
SOME GROWN‐UP JUICE?

22:54.575 --> 22:58.045
WHEN YOU HAVE A DAUGHTER
WHO DRIVES YOU TO IT.

22:58.078 --> 22:59.813
CELIA, I WANT TO GIVE YOU
A HEADS‐UP

22:59.847 --> 23:02.950
THAT DOUG KNOWS YOU'RE RUNNING
AGAINST HIM IN THE ELECTION.

23:02.983 --> 23:05.252
AND I CARE BECAUSE?

23:05.285 --> 23:07.688
HE SEEMED PRETTY UPSET,
ESPECIALLY WHEN I TOLD HIM

23:07.721 --> 23:09.489
I COULDN'T BE
HIS CAMPAIGN MANAGER.

23:09.523 --> 23:10.490
WHY NOT?

23:10.524 --> 23:11.358
WHY NOT WHAT?

23:11.391 --> 23:13.760
WHY CAN'T YOU BE
HIS CAMPAIGN MANAGER?

23:13.794 --> 23:16.496
BECAUSE YOU'RE RUNNING.
I ‐‐

23:16.530 --> 23:18.632
I JUST ASSUMED THAT...

23:18.665 --> 23:20.400
AM I YOUR CAMPAIGN MANAGER?

23:20.434 --> 23:21.201
NO.

23:21.235 --> 23:23.170
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

23:23.203 --> 23:25.339
HOW DARE YOU?
I RUN UNOPPOSED!

23:25.372 --> 23:27.407
THIS IS MY THING!
GET YOUR OWN THING!

23:27.441 --> 23:29.810
WELL, I TRIED TO GET
MY OWN THING ‐‐

23:29.843 --> 23:31.778
A LIGHT AT THE MALL
AND HILLCREEK ROAD.

23:31.812 --> 23:34.147
BUT WHEN THAT THING
DIDN'T WORK OUT,

23:34.181 --> 23:36.183
I SWITCHED TO THIS THING.

23:36.216 --> 23:38.752
I'M HOPING IN THE END
TO GET BOTH THINGS.

23:38.785 --> 23:40.020
I'M CITY COUNCILMAN DOUG!

23:40.053 --> 23:42.489
NOT AFTER THE NEXT ELECTION
YOU'RE NOT.

23:42.523 --> 23:43.490
SO YOU'RE TELLING ME

23:43.524 --> 23:45.759
YOU DON'T WANT ME
TO WORK ON YOUR CAMPAIGN?

23:45.792 --> 23:47.628
I WANT TO WIN.

23:47.661 --> 23:48.762
FUCK YOU.

23:48.795 --> 23:50.764
DEAN,
THERE'S A CHILD PRESENT.

23:50.797 --> 23:52.499
DON'T CALL ME A CHILD.

23:52.533 --> 23:53.400
I'M A CIVIC LEADER,

23:53.433 --> 23:55.269
AND YOU'RE NOT
TAKING THAT AWAY FROM ME.

23:55.302 --> 23:56.904
SHE WAS TALKING ABOUT <i>ME.</i>

23:56.937 --> 23:58.872
DOUG,
I AM SO ON YOUR SIDE.

23:58.906 --> 24:00.107
THANK YOU, COMPADRE.

24:00.140 --> 24:02.910
AND I WOULD BE HONORED
TO BE YOUR CAMPAIGN MANAGER.

24:02.943 --> 24:04.144
WE'LL SEE.

24:04.178 --> 24:05.579
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, WE'LL SEE?

24:05.612 --> 24:08.682
DO YOU THINK THAT YOU CAN TAKE
THIS PUSSY PARTY SOMEWHERE ELSE?

24:08.715 --> 24:10.317
'CAUSE WE'RE TRYING TO
WORK HERE.

24:10.350 --> 24:14.021
DAD CAN'T SAY "FUCK,"
BUT YOU CAN SAY "PUSSY"?

24:14.054 --> 24:15.789
I'LL BE IN MY ROOM.

24:15.822 --> 24:17.457
LET'S GO.

24:17.491 --> 24:19.026
YOU WILL RUE THE DAY.

24:19.059 --> 24:21.495
YEAH, YEAH, YEAH,
RUE MY ASS.

24:21.528 --> 24:22.629
