24:35.509 --> 24:37.411
DINNER IN 10 MINUTES.

24:37.444 --> 24:40.380
I'M NOT HUNGRY.
I JUST HAD VEGGIE BOOTY.

24:41.782 --> 24:43.851
WELL, YOU'RE GONNA SIT
WITH US ANYWAY.

24:43.884 --> 24:45.986
FAMILY DINNER, SO WASH UP.

24:50.824 --> 24:52.226
THE REPAIR GUY DIDN'T COME?

24:52.259 --> 24:53.794
HE WAS GONNA COME TODAY.

24:53.827 --> 24:55.562
