LUPITA HAD A HAIR APPOINTMENT.

24:55.596 --> 24:57.965
HE'LL BE HERE TOMORROW.
HEY, WHAT'S IN THE BAG?

24:57.998 --> 25:00.000
FAMILY DINNER ‐‐
ALL OF US.

25:00.033 --> 25:01.935
YEAH.
I GOT WORK TO DO, NANCE.

25:01.969 --> 25:03.470
CLEAR YOUR CRAP
OFF THE TABLE.

25:03.504 --> 25:06.006
OH, I TOLD MEGAN
I'D EAT AT HER PLACE.

25:06.039 --> 25:09.009
WELL, CALL AND TELL HER
NOT TONIGHT.

25:09.042 --> 25:10.277
I MADE PLANS.

25:10.310 --> 25:12.312
WELL, I BOUGHT CHICKEN,
AND YOU'RE MY SON,

25:12.346 --> 25:14.748
AND YOU'RE GOING TO SIT DOWN
AND WE'RE GOING TO EAT,

25:14.781 --> 25:16.216
SO CALL HER.

25:16.250 --> 25:18.118
FUNNY.

25:19.620 --> 25:20.587
TAKE THE PHONE.

25:20.621 --> 25:21.421
MOM.

25:21.455 --> 25:23.156
WE'RE GONNA HAVE
A FAMILY DINNER.

25:23.190 --> 25:24.958
YOU ARE A MEMBER
OF THIS FAMILY.

25:24.992 --> 25:28.662
TAKE THE PHONE.
CALL YOUR GIRLFRIEND ‐‐ NOW!

25:32.099 --> 25:34.201
SILAS, GET YOUR ASS
IN THIS CHAIR

25:34.234 --> 25:36.803
BEFORE I KICK IT
FROM HERE TO TUESDAY.

25:36.837 --> 25:38.739
ANDY, SET THE TABLE!

25:38.772 --> 25:40.607
GAME OVER!
WASH YOUR HANDS!

25:40.641 --> 25:42.176
SO HELP ME GOD,
I'VE HAD IT!

25:42.209 --> 25:45.679
WE'RE GONNA BE A FAMILY
IF I HAVE TO KILL ALL OF YOU!

25:45.712 --> 25:46.847
YOU HEAR ME?!

25:46.880 --> 25:48.615
FINE.
I'LL EAT TWICE.

25:48.649 --> 25:50.751
EAT SEVEN TIMES!
I DON'T CARE.

25:50.784 --> 25:52.586
AS LONG AS YOU EAT ONCE
WITH US.

25:52.619 --> 25:55.389
YOU'RE REALLY INVESTED
IN THIS CHICKEN, AREN'T YOU?

25:55.422 --> 25:57.257
SHUT UP!

25:59.860 --> 26:01.595
SEE?

26:01.628 --> 26:02.896
NICE.

26:02.930 --> 26:04.631
DINNER.

26:04.665 --> 26:06.867
SO...

26:06.900 --> 26:08.735
HOW WAS EVERYONE'S DAY?

26:08.769 --> 26:11.505
I GOT A "B"
ON MY FRENCH TEST.

26:11.538 --> 26:12.906
OH, TRèS BIEN.

26:12.940 --> 26:14.041
SILAS?

26:14.074 --> 26:15.242
I TAKE SPANISH.

26:15.275 --> 26:17.344
DID YOU GET
ANY TESTS BACK TODAY?

26:17.377 --> 26:18.612
NO.

26:18.645 --> 26:23.016
I'M WRITING ABOUT
WHAT BEING A JEW MEANS TO ME.

26:23.050 --> 26:24.585
AND IF I WRITE WELL,

26:24.618 --> 26:26.787
I'LL BE ACCEPTED
INTO RABBINICAL SCHOOL.

26:26.820 --> 26:30.157
AND IF I DON'T...

26:30.190 --> 26:31.892
I'LL BE SHIPPED OVERSEAS
TO DIE.

26:31.925 --> 26:33.360
SO FAR I'VE WRITTEN,

26:33.393 --> 26:35.329
"BEING A JEW MEANS
I HAVE NO FORESKIN,

26:35.362 --> 26:37.764
AND I MAY BE
A TAY‐SACHS CARRIER."

26:37.798 --> 26:40.534
SO, UH...

26:40.567 --> 26:42.369
I THINK I'M GONNA DIE.

26:42.402 --> 26:44.137
WHAT'S TAY‐SACHS?

26:44.171 --> 26:47.241
IT'S A FATAL GENETIC
LIPID‐STORAGE DISORDER,

26:47.274 --> 26:48.809
PREVALENT AMONG
EUROPEAN JEWS.

26:48.842 --> 26:50.210
YOU DON'T HAVE TO WORRY
ABOUT IT.

26:50.244 --> 26:52.279
IF YOU HAD IT,
YOU'D ALREADY BE DEAD.
COOL.

26:52.312 --> 26:53.747
SEE?

26:53.780 --> 26:55.582
LOOK HOW WE'RE LEARNING
NEW THINGS.

26:55.616 --> 26:59.353
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

26:59.386 --> 27:02.055
WE'RE NOT GOING TO ANSWER
THE PHONE DURING DINNER.

27:02.089 --> 27:03.957
