27:03.991 --> 27:05.859
I MEAN IT.

27:05.893 --> 27:08.161
Shane: Hello.
You've reached the Botwins.

27:08.195 --> 27:10.797
We're not home right now,
but if you leave us a message,

27:10.831 --> 27:12.699
we'll come home right away.

27:12.733 --> 27:14.234
